    <h2>Version 0.5.2 - Minor improvements release</h2>
    <p>01/10/2019 <a href="https://github.com/Gogoku7/LivestreamProductionManager/projects/4">GitHub Version Project</a></p>
    <p>No Public update video</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Implemented Focus toggles</li>
        <ul>
            <li>Focus toggles allows you to disable and hide UI elements that the user does not interact with in the Fighting Games Manager user interface</li>
            <ul>
                <li>The Focus toggle on the Manage Tournament panel disables and hides the WebSocket clients monitor and Error monitor</li>
                <ul>
                    <li>It's recommended to only toggle these off when you are sure of security and bugs</li>
                </ul>
                <li>The Focus toggle on the Manage Competitors panel disables and hides the Competitors data monitor, CSS monitor and JSON monitor</li>
