        <li>Improved styling around Crews and Squad Strike Checkboxes, they are now always properly centered under the label text</li>
        <li>Changed the WebSocket communication</li>
        <ul>
            <li>The Fighting Games Manager is now properly added to the WebSocket clients monitor through the WebSocket</li>
            <li>"overlayType" has been renamed to "clientType" in the WebSocket communication and through most of the application</li>
        </ul>
        <li>Improved the code of moving Commentators up and down</li>
        <li>Added the missing image files used in the Super Smash Bros. Ultimate Crews and Squad Strike Overlays to the Solution file, this helps deploying to IIS</li>
    </ul>

