    <h2>Version 0.5</h2>
    <p>11/08/2019 - <a href="https://github.com/Gogoku7/LivestreamProductionManager/projects/2">GitHub Version Project</a></p>
    <p>Public update video: <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=39qSgfExyx0">Livestream Production Manager - Tournament Streaming (Open Source) - Public Update 5 (Version 0.5)</a></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Moved the Solution folder one layer closer to the root of the Repo, resulting in shorter file paths</li>
        <li>It is now possible to submit a "No character" and "No port" option when submitting updates without it becoming a default value</li>
        <li>A Plus and Minus button have been added to quickly increase or decrease the score by one</li>
        <li>Skin picker has been implemented for Super Smash Bros. Wii U and Ultimate, for the formats Singles and Doubles</li>
        <li>General settings have been implemented</li>
        <ul>
            <li>Select which theme the application has by default</li>
            <li>Select whether switching themes should use a smooth transition</li>
        </ul>
        <li>The dropdown menu's in the navigation bar at the top of the page don't add a '#' to the url in the url bar anymore</li>
